341
00:55:16,017 --> 00:55:20,147
The fact that politicians sanction
a cross-border-system...

342
00:55:20,288 --> 00:55:24,952
...is sometimes due to ignorance.

343
00:55:25,694 --> 00:55:27,685
Those who understand...

344
00:55:28,296 --> 00:55:32,027
...care only about the very
short period of their career.

345
00:55:32,167 --> 00:55:34,362
They are not interested
in what happens after them.

346
00:55:34,503 --> 00:55:38,496
This short-term attitude...

347
00:55:38,640 --> 00:55:42,974
...the lack of a will to take
responsibility for the long term...

348
00:55:43,111 --> 00:55:47,275
- Knowing it will be up to others
to resolve the problems later...

349
00:55:47,415 --> 00:55:51,044
...is characteristic
of the neo-liberal era.

350
00:55:51,286 --> 00:55:53,186
In the neo-liberal era...

351
00:55:53,321 --> 00:55:56,813
...everything is reduced...

